answerText: New England Patriots [accept either][10] This former quarterback for the Patriots was recently inducted into the team's Hall of Fame. He played for three years at Washington State before playing for the Patriots until 2001, when a hit by the Jets' Mo Lewis sidelined him and opened up the quarterback position for Tom Brady.
